OL,6,FLocal children from nearby Kirk Balk
OL,7,FHigh School unveiled the 6ft steel
OL,8,Fartwork near the terraced house Hines
OL,9,Fcalled home on Monday, 20 May.
OL,11,FIt stands close to many of the
OL,12,Flocations used in the 1968 film,
OL,13,Fincluding Casper's fish and chip shop.
OL,15,FCllr Robin Franklin said: "The
OL,16,Fpoignant story of Kes and Billy Casper
OL,17,Fis known the world over thanks to the
OL,18,Fwonderful writing of Barry Hines.
