OL,6,F"We were pleased to unveil the
OL,7,Fsculpture of the two friends in
OL,8,FBarnsley town centre in 2022, but it
OL,9,Fis only fitting that they are also
OL,10,Fformally remembered close to where
OL,11,FBarry lived.
OL,13,F"This is a fantastic new addition to
OL,14,FHoyland Common, and I hope people will
OL,15,Fbe inspired and proud when they see
OL,16,Fit."
OL,18,FThe sculpture was designed by Barnsley
OL,19,Fartist Patrick Murphy, who has also
OL,20,Fbeen involved in other tributes to
OL,21,FHines' work.
